Text: Kevins Lunch Cc LNotesnsf You are cordially invited to a luncheon in honor of Kevin Cousineau in order to say farewell Kevins last day will be Friday July th Please see email below for details Forwarded by Christy WireEWCEnron on AM Nagwa Elkachouty PM To Ralph NRON Robert NRON Claire nron David NRON Emil NRON David NRON David nron Kirk nron Andre NRON Andre NRON Alaadin nron Joe NRON Craig NRON Kim nron Mark NRON Philippe NRON Tom NRON Rain NRON Mark NRON Stan NRON Mark NRON Stan NRON Ronald NRON Michael nron Tim nron Eric NRON Brian Miller nronxgate Kim nron Garth nron Lourine NRON Joel NRON Christy nron Kathy NRON cc Kevin NRON Subject Kevins Lunch We are having lunch at Domingos on Thursday July at lunch time noon time Be sure to be there to say farewell to a Great Man Thanks Nagwa
